            <abstract>
                <p>A short list of the commemoration dates of the Apostles, the Evangelists,
                    and, occasionally, a few other saints (see the two examples provided in the edition).
                    For more extensive calendars, see <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3123Calend">Calendar of saints, arranged according to their feast day</ref>.
                    For unidentified calendars, see <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/NAR0005calend">Calendar of saint commemorations</ref>.</p>
            </abstract>
